data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This single level 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence boasts a charming and family-friendly design. With a oversized 3-car garage, U-shaped driveway, and a fully fenced backyard; this property offers convenience and security that's hard to beat. Step inside, and you'll find a well-designed living space that's perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. But that's not all! This home also features a versatile mother-in-law suite that can be used for extended family, guests, or even as a home office. It's all about flexibility!Enjoy outdoor living in the private, fenced backyard, perfect for playtime, gardening, or simply unwinding in the fresh air.Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a home that combines comfort, convenience, and versatility. Make it yours today!Home is recently renovated and most features are under 2 years old - HVAC, Water Heater, Windows, Kitchen and AppliancesGarage is 45 x 30 - MIL Suite is 15 x 30 and is framed, wired and plumbed for a 1-bedroom, 1-bath with kitchen and living area.
